name: Public-And-Transit
description: A system of transport that is available for use by the general public, typically operated by a government agency or a public authority

name: Transit-Agency
description: An organization responsible for planning, financing, and operating public transport services

name: Ridership-Data
description: Data related to the number of passengers using the transit system

name: Service-Data
description: Data related to transit services offered

name: Schedule-Data
description: Data related to transit schedules

name: Routing-Data
description: Data related to transit routes and stops

name: Transit-Vehicle
description: A vehicle used for public transport

name: Bus
description: A road vehicle designed to carry many passengers

name: Seating-Capacities
description: Data related to the seating capacities of the bus

name: Revenue-Data
description: Data related to the revenue generated by the bus

name: Revenue-Hours
description: Data related to the number of hours the bus generates revenue

name: Revenue-Miles
description: Data related to the number of miles the bus generates revenue

name: Train
description: A road vehicle designed to carry many passengers over longer distances

name: Safety-Data
description: Data related to train safety

name: Collision-Data
description: Data related to train collisions

name: Equity-Data-Hub
description: Data related to transit equity, available through an Equity Data Hub

name: Security
description: Procedures, devices, and personnel for protecting the public and the transit system

name: Access-Control
description: Systems and procedures for controlling access to the transit system

name: CCTV
description: Closed-circuit television systems used for monitoring the transit system

name: Service
description: Provision of transit services to passengers

name: Collision-Data
description: Data related to transit collisions

name: Schedule-Data
description: Data related to transit schedules

name: Route-Data
description: Data related to transit routes and stops

name: Unlinked-Passenger-Trips-Data
description: Data related to unlinked passenger trips, including boardings and alightings
